      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@\n+created: 2026-01-08\n+title: Autonomous Commit Workflows\n+intro: >-\n+  This release introduces autonomous commit workflows that automatically split unrelated\n+  changes into separate commits without prompting. The new `/git:address-pr-comments`\n+  command systematically addresses GitHub PR review comments, creating commits and\n+  resolving threads automatically. The commit workflow now includes expanded static\n+  checks (linters, type checkers, formatters) before staging changes. Several bugfixes\n+  improve multi-line review comment handling and branch pushing reliability."
